IShoppingMallFraudDetection.description:
Tracks suspicious activities detected by AI fraud detection systems within the shopping mall platform.

Enables auditing and investigation of potential security incidents to enhance platform trust and user safety.

Records include customer and order references, detection types, confidence levels, resolutions, and timestamps.

